    "The 8-puzzle is particularly well-suited to our investigation because it is a well-studied problem in AI [29], it provides a controllable and predictable environment in which the model must track the board state and obey strict rules, and it demands non-trivial long-term planning because solutions are unlikely to be found through local or random actions alone.",
